Subject: [PATCH] wifi: ath12k: Dump PDEV transmit rate HTT stats
Git-commit: ba42b22aa336c3ea0bd6f9c606f70a35a278bd61
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Support to dump PDEV transmit rate stats through HTT debugfs stats type 9.

